{"tid":1564934,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美財長指特朗普預備隨時上調中國貨關稅 香港問題非談判一部分","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T03:12:34.000Z","uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a19296166322a3843cda3b4daa271bbeab2b5459","tid":1564934,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"美國財長努欽接受《CNBC》訪問時表示，美國總統特朗普可在任何時間與中國達成貿易協議，但必須對美國企業及工人最有利。他又指特朗普預備維持現有關稅，及在需要時增加關稅。<br />\n<br />\n對於中國購買農產品，努欽稱美國希望中國購買。他指貿易問題不止於出售大豆，但美國希望向中國出售大豆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n努欽又表示，香港的示威並非中美貿易談判的一部分。(fc/da)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.965500/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.965500%2F2&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=5968e548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.965500/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757cfcb8c8de95901a0f6a54b7f52c9fc2ce9706","tid":1564934,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" c